  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "题目描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "有 $n$ 枚纪念币排成一排。初始时，所有硬币都是正面朝上。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "在一次操作中，你可以选择恰好 $k$ 枚连续硬币，并将它们全部翻转。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "给定最终状态 $s$，描述每枚硬币是正面朝上还是反面朝上，判断是否可以通过若干次操作（包括零次操作）从初始状态达到该状态。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输入描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第一行包含一个正整数 $T$ $(1 \\le T \\le 2 \\times 10^5)$，表示测试用例的数量。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于每个测试用例：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第一行包含两个正整数 $n, k$ $(1 \\le k \\le n \\le 2 \\times 10^5)$。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第二行包含一个长度为 $n$ 的字符串 $s$，由 0 和 1 组成。$s_i = 0$ 表示最终状态中第 $i$ 枚硬币正面朝上，$s_i = 1$ 表示最终状态中第 $i$ 枚硬币反面朝上。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "保证单个测试集中所有测试用例的 $n$ 之和不超过 $2 \\times 10^5$。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输出描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于每个测试用例，如果该状态可达，则输出一行包含 Yes，否则输出 No。答案不区分大小写。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "样例",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "输入",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "text",
              "code": "2\n5 3\n01110\n3 2\n100",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输出",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "text",
              "code": "YES\nNO",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "无",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n, k; cin >> n >> k;\n\tstring s; cin >> s; s = ' ' + s;\n\tvar a = vector<int>(n + 2);\n\tvar d = vector<int>(n + 2);\n\tint sum = 0;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tsum += d[i];\n\t\ta[i] += sum;\n\t\tint tar = (s[i] == '1');\n\t\tint now = (a[i] & 1);\n\t\tif (now != tar) {\n\t\t\tint l = i, r = i + k - 1;\n\t\t\tif (r > n) {\n\t\t\t\tcout << \"NO\" << endl;\n\t\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\td[r + 1] -= 1;\n\t\t\tsum += 1;\n\t\t\ta[i] += 1;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tcout << \"YES\" << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
